{"tha-ap246:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap246:0.2":"Tuvaradayakavagga ","tha-ap246:0.3":"4 Viravapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap246:1.1":"“Khinasavasahassehi, ","tha-ap246:1.2":"niyyati lokanayako; ","tha-ap246:1.3":"Viravapupphamadaya, ","tha-ap246:1.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap246:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap246:2.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap246:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap246:2.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap246:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap246:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap246:3.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap246:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma viravapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap246:5.1":"Viravapupphiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}